longBusinessSummary: Ajanta Pharma Limited, together with its subsidiaries, a pharmaceutical formulation company, development, manufacturing and marketing of speciality pharmaceutical finished dosages. It also offers chronic, and acute therapies; and tablets, capsules, injectables, inhalers, ointments, creams and liquids. The company engages in molecule and therapeutic segments. The company serves in India, Africa, Asia, the United States, and internationally. Ajanta Pharma Limited was founded in 1973 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India.
